-- =============================================================================
-- NPC BUSINESS PAYMENT TERMINAL
-- ServicePaymentTerminal
--
-- v1.3.0-NPC-BUSINESS-TAVERN
--
-- Combined MineColonies business transaction collector.
--
-- Handles:
--   * Dining Hall / Restaurant meals:
--       - detects positive citizen saturation changes
--       - charges the citizen account through hospitality_meal_payment
--       - hospitality company receives the meal revenue
--       - treasury covers citizen shortfalls through the bank handler
--
--   * State Tavern / Inn nightly stays:
--       - treats the Tavern as a state-owned enterprise
--       - charges one nightly lodging fee per visible guest/citizen per MC day
--       - known citizens/accounts pay into treasury:quid_bank
--       - unknown visitors are external guests credited to treasury
--       - uses tavern_night_payment so GDP/transaction stats can count it
--
-- Pricing:
--   * Dining meals use quote_service_price("dining_meal") when available.
--   * Tavern stays use quote_service_price("tavern_night") when available.
--   * Both therefore move with the bank's inflation / sector index model.
--
-- Requires ServerSideAccounts with:
--   * quote_service_price
--   * hospitality_meal_payment
--   * tavern_night_payment
-- =============================================================================

